Version 1.0 - released 2014-07-01
* fixed vulnerability under unsupported CMSimple_XH versions, where the plugin
  administration didn't require authentication

Version 1.0rc1 - released 2014-04-15
* fixed bug, where a fatal error occured on older PHP versions (reported by
  Simmyne)
* removed unintentional requirement on CSRF protection
* added check whether the form has an amount_field (inspired by Simmyne)

Version 1.0beta1 - released 2014-03-21
* initial release
